Class Carta

java.lang.Object
com.example.gameuno.Models.Carta
public class Carta extends Object
This class Carta contains its attributes such as color, valor, nombreArchivo and getters This class Carta contains methods that differentiate the types of cards as well as getters and setters methods for temporary colors
